title: Bug 116564 - The title of hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", now it changes with settings.
OB: When clicking on the "OK" button and reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title becomes "www.actuate.com".
EB: The expected behavior is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options".
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Click on the "OK" button.
2. Reopen the hyperlink builder and observe the title change to "www.actuate.com" instead of "Hyperlink Options".
